               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra (only St Mary); name of the protagonist, name of the donor Wäldä Mikaʾel (only on fol. 2rb); incipit of the text and of each miracle; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.&#xD;
The title ʾabunä is added to the names of the donors by secondary hand in deep vermilion (fols. 4va, 5va, 7rb).</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
